{"tid":1943173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港民研：77%人反林鄭","createTime":"2020-03-25T13:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T18:04:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9f60ff6667c064a249be842c78f2e60adb411f","tid":1943173,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200325/KOLLSWH5UX3XLYTVXQEWSSWLCA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200325%2FKOLLSWH5UX3XLYTVXQEWSSWLCA%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Y%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=436d233b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200325%2FKOLLSWH5UX3XLYTVXQEWSSWLCA%2F&h=864800b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200325/KOLLSWH5UX3XLYTVXQEWSSWLCA/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民研：77%人反林鄭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200325/large/1585066921_da15.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200325%2Flarge%2F1585066921_da15.gif&h=991bc5be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港民意研究計劃最新民調顯示，77%港人反對林鄭月娥出任特首。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港民意研究所最新民調顯示，特首林鄭月娥民望雖回穩，但仍有77%港人反對她做特首，最新評分仍然只有22.3分，民望淨值為負64個百分點，兩項民望數字與半個月前分別不大。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：發燒青年偷走食車仔麵<br />\n<br />\n對政府滿意度回升<br />\n<br />\n民意研究所於上周二至四（17日至20日）訪問約1,000人，支持林鄭出任特首的比率維持在12%；反對她出任特首的比率高達77%，較上次調查下跌3個百分點。市民對特區政府表現的滿意率顯著回升，由9%升至17%，不滿率由83%下跌至68%，滿意率淨值為負51個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n市民對政府的信任度亦顯著改善。信任政府比率升至25%，較上月上升10個百分點，不信任度則高企62%，較上月下跌14個百分點。在民生、經濟、政治的滿意度方面，市民對現時民生、經濟及政治狀況的滿意淨值分別為負51、負58及負74個百分點，同樣較上個月明顯回升。<br />\n<br />\n出席民調記者會的民主黨前主席、港大榮譽助理教授楊森認為，市民對政府評分上升，但林鄭評分「毫無寸進」，形容是特別現象，反映市民對林鄭的看法已經定性，由反送中到抗疫，看得出林鄭「唔聽民意、剛愎自用」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姚國雄"},{"pid":"0afe6d40b956acb9d99b3bf74a0d75e8e4417a11","tid":1943173,"uid":68080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"市民對特區政府表現的滿意率顯著回升，由9%升至17%，不滿率由83%下跌至68%，滿意率淨值為負51個百分點。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過黎緊經濟繼續差<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fcb1573e8fa23afefa23899f1bce7720fdf2d6","tid":1943173,"uid":57636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"嗰12%支持係咩人嚟?<br />\n定係已經覺得到咗呢個時候，邊個做都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係真心支持的話，真係想認識下呢類係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4e45535d17cd70831cd1440e052be8a5ba79ef","tid":1943173,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9fcb1573e8fa23afefa23899f1bce7720fdf2d6","tid":1943173,"uid":57636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"嗰12%支持係咩人嚟?<br />\n定係已經覺得到咗呢個時候，邊個做都無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係真心支持的話，真係想認識下呢類係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"藍屍基本盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b6cef45592089c9aa98df65d01fafde04e7fec","tid":1943173,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"77% 咁撚少 ?  向太話有 90% 架喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aa6d468eb4350646c34ec64801114fa42c031a","tid":1943173,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13feed712c501e884955a112c609d3681d139962","tid":1943173,"